      "content": "Do not take 1200mg of ibuprofen all at once; that is a very high dose and could cause serious stomach issues. Since you are in pain and can't see a doctor, try a combination of a heating pad and a few doses of acetaminophen, following the package directions for each. For immediate relief, try a gentle stretching routine or a very hot shower to see if that helps loosen things up for the night.",
