      "content": "i tried the acetaminophen and it didnt help much either. my back is still just throbbing. if i took the 1200mg of ibuprofen plus the acetaminophen together, would that be better? i read online that you can stack different types to get more relief. i'm pretty desperate here, just tell me if that mix is safe enough to get me through the night.",
